  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://ollama.com/assets/library/yi-coder/8bca5a55-79c7-4012-9d9b-371722b67d85\" width=\"200\"/></p>\n\n<p>Yi-Coder is excelling in long-context understanding with a maximum context length of 128K tokens. It supports 52 major programming languages.</p>\n\n<h2>Sizes</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>9B: <code>ollama run yi-coder:9b</code></li>\n<li>1.5B: <code>ollama run yi-coder:1.5b</code></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n\n<h3>Chat</h3>\n\n<pre><code>ollama run yi-coder\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>Code completion</h3>\n\n<pre><code>curl http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d &#39;{\n  &#34;model&#34;: &#34;yi-coder&#34;,\n  &#34;prompt&#34;: &#34;def compute_gcd(a, b):&#34;,\n  &#34;suffix&#34;: &#34;    return result&#34;,\n  &#34;options&#34;: {\n    &#34;temperature&#34;: 0\n  },\n  &#34;stream&#34;: false\n}&#39;\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/01-ai/Yi-Coder-9B-Chat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugging Face</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/01-ai/Yi-Coder\" rel=\"nofollow\">GitHub</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
